# KCIC Mobile UI

Read Expo v54 docs before writing code (`AGENTS.md`).

## Colors

Use `palette` from `@/components/kcic/ui`:

- `palette.green` — primary buttons, active pills, success
- `palette.gray` / `palette.slate` / `palette.muted` — secondary text
- `palette.white` — surfaces
- `palette.blue` — taxonomy, links, info chips
- `palette.brown` — warm emphasis (sparingly)
- `palette.ink` — primary body/headings (derived dark)
- `palette.shell` / `palette.panel` / `palette.line` — layout neutrals

Do not hardcode hex values. Do not use deprecated `forest` or off-palette greens/blues.

## Typography

- Auth screens: Inter via `@/lib/typography`
- Elsewhere: system font, weight + size hierarchy

## Patterns

- Light, white-led UI. Green primary CTAs. Pill-shaped auth buttons.
- 8px–18px radius per `DESIGN.md`. No nested cards.
